edge cases, invalid arguments, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;That being said that's not a hard rule and the patch is welcome,
could you please commit it yourself via docrails? I'll merge it
into master later. docrails has public write access, just push the
changes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
